Custom Functions in HDL
✎ Recommended: Modify the module declaration to remove these port types, or create a wrapper file around the module to contain only the supported port types for packaging your design. As an example, the following module declaration contains unsupported complex and split port types:
module top({in1, in2}, out[0], out[1]);
input in1, in2;
output [1:0] out;
endmodule
